headline: BD to Present at Goldman Sachs 46th Annual Global Healthcare Conference
summary: BD (Becton, Dickinson and Company) (NYSE: BDX), a leading global medical technology company, today announced that it will present at the Goldman Sachs 46th Annual Global Healthcare Conference on Monday, June 9, 2025 at 2:00 pm Eastern Time.
